{"tid":2463912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《鬼滅之刃》真人版找誰演？韓國網友瘋討論：BTS、TWICE、金宇彬都被點名！","createTime":"2021-03-27T05:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T06:50:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6281897ceb090ed24377e95b813eb3190c2db6","tid":2463912,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_6b0012547dab25a78391376ad7b0ffa9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_6b0012547dab25a78391376ad7b0ffa9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901301.jpg&h=4eb7d7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風靡全球的日本動畫《鬼滅之刃》在韓國同樣吹起旋風，甚至網友們開始紛紛討論劇中角色如果拍攝真人版，可以考慮找誰來演出？答案令人會心一笑，大家覺得像不像呢？<br />\n<br />\n＃竈門炭治郎：BTS防彈少年團柾國<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9c127f94094a9a7f6726e7aff97dce5e/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901302.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9c127f94094a9a7f6726e7aff97dce5e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901302.png&h=e4d2e87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_74b9cdfe263498b1f27cadf6bfd2369d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_74b9cdfe263498b1f27cadf6bfd2369d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901286.jpg&h=97929f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, TVDaily<br />\n為救妹妹而與鬼為敵的竈門炭治郎，有著圓圓的大眼睛與白皙皮膚，其實就是美男界的代表，而且他的善良以及他圓滑的個性，令許多網友們推崇BTS防彈少年團的田柾國最相似。<br />\n<br />\n＃竈門彌豆子：IZ*ONE張員瑛<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_554a1a52d68dd0b7f73600a899cd068f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901303.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_554a1a52d68dd0b7f73600a899cd068f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901303.png&h=6ae68fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_aaa9ae78d4a7ebe43bdb350980bab02d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_aaa9ae78d4a7ebe43bdb350980bab02d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901289.jpg&h=11dd3d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, TVDaily<br />\n劇中咬著竹筒的彌豆子時常露出惹人憐愛的眼神，加上長髮造型，其實有滿多女星都有可能給人相似的感覺，但大家特別推崇張員瑛的可愛氣息與無辜眼神，最像彌豆子。<br />\n<br />\n＃宇髓天元：NCT Lucas<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ea568f890fa70f5f26b1bf9d4a9d65d4/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901304.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ea568f890fa70f5f26b1bf9d4a9d65d4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901304.png&h=fb120720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2d6e9e939a83dc88dd8b73a7009919f9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2d6e9e939a83dc88dd8b73a7009919f9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901291.jpg&h=a65e5ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, TVDaily<br />\n擁有三位夫人的宇隨天元，外貌有著相當華麗的打扮，眼周塗上特色紅色色彩還鑲上了水鑽，華麗的外貌下有著爽朗的個性，還能夠用壯碩的肌肉強行讓心臟停止。NCT成員Lucas有著中泰混血帥氣外型與壯壯的身材，被大家喻為是宇隨天元真人版。<br />\n<br />\n＃甘露寺蜜璃：TWICE Sana<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_67263741e5b142ff10c47ab078b58c12/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901305.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_67263741e5b142ff10c47ab078b58c12%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901305.png&h=e9e25c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_374a7b0d324ddbf145aa51450bdba85a/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_374a7b0d324ddbf145aa51450bdba85a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901288.jpg&h=8bfbe616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, TVDaily<br />\n擁有淺綠色的大眼睛以及泛紅的雙頰，性格很活潑開朗但容易害羞臉紅，造成汗水不停流，超級可愛又討喜的她，被大家認為與TWICE中的成員Sana最相似。<br />\n<br />\n＃伊黑小芭內：長髮李鐘碩<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_686688d8f09ade5a3e25d8b7561b2985/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901313.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_686688d8f09ade5a3e25d8b7561b2985%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901313.png&h=eb7977fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c3f3aded222e7b98724d443b435839e2/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c3f3aded222e7b98724d443b435839e2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901287.jpg&h=64f0a515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, AMAN Project<br />\n說到甘露寺蜜璃就不能忘了提到暗戀著她的蛇柱伊黑小芭內，他生來就有兩種顏色－綠色與金色的瞳孔，脖子上總是纏繞著一條白蛇，給人相當神秘的魅力，與最近留著長髮演出《魔女2》的李鐘碩有幾分神似。<br />\n<br />\n＃不死川實彌：金宇彬<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_13dc161aaa5f252ce0049adfac1c476f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901312.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_13dc161aaa5f252ce0049adfac1c476f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901312.png&h=bd1238ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_13a6603480027e8bcbecd05894e4dc8a/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_13a6603480027e8bcbecd05894e4dc8a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901295.jpg&h=ae2c1d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, TVDaily<br />\n頂著白色刺蝟頭，臉上與身上都佈滿傷痕的不死川實彌，暴戾性格耍狠的時候，大家認為金宇彬最能表現出這種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n＃煉獄杏壽郎：羅勳兒<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0cc028ea6f91488df14d92703f3876a1/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901316.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0cc028ea6f91488df14d92703f3876a1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901316.png&h=08d77eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5e8594b7814791b6fd0a3ba261c31c83/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-26/134500-901314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5e8594b7814791b6fd0a3ba261c31c83%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-26%2F134500-901314.jpg&h=05082aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片:Viu Hong Kong, TVDaily<br />\n角色造型鮮明的煉獄杏壽郎，是鬼殺隊中最愛照顧人的大哥，劍眉與炯炯有神的眼睛，展現領袖氣息，網友們提名資深韓國歌手羅勳兒，認為他充滿陽剛氣息，是男人中的男人。<br />\n<br />\n《鬼滅之刃》封圖及截圖自：Viu Hong Kong"},{"pid":"3af921fa74cf24888c6d907aced839d25bf995d8","tid":2463912,"uid":8812,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"屌大哥想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a22bd58be9ff3442383ac46ff4d654531b138f1","tid":2463912,"uid":12782,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"成日覺得港版開拍 <br />\n一定要揾Lokman做炎柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣樣咁濟"},{"pid":"cdf83d80a615f0bca34593f4ea9ba5ae1bd548ec","tid":2463912,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"瑛妹很可愛😭😭😭"},{"pid":"79dc318b181ee8845215e2062d09d045790f53b7","tid":2463912,"uid":163937,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"sana對波咁細"},{"pid":"7329c4f40c5ae30c34cd45c06d80b232574b03f0","tid":2463912,"uid":48783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"啲人係咪覓腸自己揀架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a738